Starscream thanled the Matirx. He didn't know if Goldeneye was being 
nice to him, or actually didn't here anything. But she would keep her 
mouth shut. Starscream went to his quarters and read a bit about the 
area where the cave was located.

Vulois decsended deeper and deep down the tunnel into darkness.

"Eye lights, on!"

Vulois' eyes lit up, guiding the way. He came to a crossroads.

"Left...no right!Wait, it's left. Right, it's left."

Vulois headed down the left passage. He yelled back.

"Windrazor, Terradive, come on! We'll be there soon!"
